lang_translation_comment: Might contain some auto translated phrases. If you'd like to improve the translation, please, email dev@airapport.com

CODE_aaa_untranslated.TXID_CAP_BACKUPSEXPLANATION: Backup lets you store and revert your current game world, while it has no effect on the currencies which are linked to your account (Rubies)
CODE_aaa_untranslated.TXID_CAP_REWARD2TESTER: During the development we have changed the game core, so, you have fresh start. But we give you a boost to regain your progress faster

CODE_aaa_untranslated.TXID_UMP_ADSONLYREW: Game does not show ads without your approval
CODE_aaa_untranslated.TXID_UMP_CONSENTEXPL: Please, give your consent to let the game load advertisement which will provide rewards.
